There are similar fonts available, but there is something that strikes me as handlettered about your sample.

[http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/founder/fz-zhan-bi-hei-m22/](http://web.archive.org/web/20071203185004/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/founder/fz-zhan-bi-hei-m22/ "http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/founder/fz-zhan-bi-hei-m22/")

There are many similar looking at your sample, I would guess the Cherry part at least was handlettered, the r’s look different and overall clumsy. Here are some others in that theme  
 [http://www.dafont.com/theme.php?cat=201&page=2](http://web.archive.org/web/20071203185004/http:/www.dafont.com/theme.php?cat=201&page=2 "http://www.dafont.com/theme.php?cat=201&page=2")
